OL,3,CFour men and a teenager jailed for
OL,4,Cmurder of Middlesborough man
OL,6,FFour men have been jailed for life for
OL,7,Ftheir roles in the murder of 27-year-
OL,8,Fold Jordan Hogg in Hemlington,
OL,9,FMiddlesborough. Kaiden McIver, 17, has
OL,10,Fbeen jailed for a minimum of 17 years.
OL,12,FSidney Bashford, 29, Oliver Connelly,
OL,13,F28, and Ryan Moore, 23, forced their
OL,14,Fway into Jordan Hogg's home armed with
OL,15,Fknives and machetes just before
OL,16,Fmidnight on 28 February last year.
