OL,6,FMeanwhile, Michael Charville, 44, and
OL,7,FMcIver were prosecuted under joint
OL,8,Fenterprise for assisting or
OL,9,Fencouraging the attack whilst
OL,10,Fremaining outside the property.
OL,12,FBashford slashed Jordan's neck with a
OL,13,Fknife, and although Jordan did manage
OL,14,Fto alert a neighbour, he died at the
OL,15,Fscene.
