OL,6,FSeveral days after the murder,
OL,7,FBashford fled the UK and boarded a
OL,8,Fferry to France. Officials secured an
OL,9,Finternational arrest warrant and
OL,10,FFrench police arrested him in
OL,11,FCherbourg.
OL,13,FBashford was returned to the UK on 27
OL,14,FMarch and arrested on his arrival at
OL,15,FHeathrow Airport.
