OL,3,CFour men and a teenager jailed for
OL,4,Cmurder of Middlesborough man
OL,6,FThe prosecution argued that the attack
OL,7,Fcame after an e-bike belonging to
OL,8,FBashford was stolen earlier that
OL,9,Fevening by another man, someone they
OL,10,Fknew was not Jordan Hogg. Bashford and
OL,11,Fthe others were told and started
OL,12,Fsearching for the person responsible.
OL,13,FIt remans unclear why Jordan was
OL,14,Fwrongly targeted.
