OL,3,CFour men and a teenager jailed for
OL,4,Cmurder of Middlesborough man
OL,6,FAfter sentencing, Jordan's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "To know these men will now
OL,8,Fserve a significant time in prison
OL,9,Fbrings a form of justice for Jordan
OL,10,Fand all of us as a family. However, no
OL,11,Famount of time will ever make up for
OL,12,Fhow they cruelly took Jordan away from
OL,13,Fus, and most importantly his daughter,
OL,14,Fand the immeasurable loss we all feel.
OL,16,F"Jordan was a funny, loving and a
OL,17,Ftruly special man who loved his
OL,18,Fdaughter beyond measure. Life will
OL,19,Fnever be the same without him.
