OL,6,F"We want to take this opportunity to
OL,7,Fexpress how truly grateful we are as a
OL,8,Ffamily to Cleveland Police. The
OL,9,Fdetectives have worked exceptionally
OL,10,Fhard from the very beginning to ensure
OL,11,Fthese men were rightfully found
OL,12,Fguilty."
OL,14,FSenior Investigating Officer DCI Chris
OL,15,FPringle said: "The sentences handed
OL,16,Fdown to these violent men will never
OL,17,Fbe enough for Jordan's family and
OL,18,Ffriends who have all been left
OL,19,Fdevastated by his death.
