OL,6,F"Their intent to cause the harm that
OL,7,Fthey did that night over a stolen bike
OL,8,Fis beyond comprehension and
OL,9,Funjustifiable.
OL,11,F"It is only the long sentences they
OL,12,Fwill now serve behind bars that acts
OL,13,Fas the justice they deserve.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts continue to be with
OL,16,FJordan's family as they navigate their
OL,17,Fway through their loss.
